---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const blogData = Astro.locals.blogData;
const pageDescription = blogData?.description;
const ogImage = blogData?.image ?? "/bimaakbar-og-default.png";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description={pageDescription} image={ogImage} url="https://bimaakbar.my.id/privacy-policy">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="mb-4">
      This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information from visitors of our website
      <strong>bimaakbar.web.id</strong> (referred to as "we", "our", or "the site").
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Our blog does not directly collect any personal information from users. However, we use third-party services
      such as:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li><strong>Blogger API v3</strong>: to fetch and display blog posts from our Blogger site.</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong>: for website hosting and caching.</li>
      <li><strong>Google Fonts / Fonts CDN</strong>: for font rendering (if applicable).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. Cookies</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We do not set cookies directly. However, third-party services such as Google may use cookies to manage API
      access or track analytics (if analytics are enabled in the future).
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We do not share your data with any third parties. All content displayed is publicly available through
      Blogger.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Our blog may include links to external sites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of
      those websites.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with the updated
      date.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">6. Contact</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      For any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:
      <br />
      <strong>contact@bimaakbar.web.id</strong>
    </p>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Last updated: July 5, 2025</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
